Verses.Text:
Dolo taara dɔnbaaw ɲɛ,
Fɔ ka se Bɛtilɛhɛmu;
U ye Masakɛ Yesu Ala Denkɛ ye.

Ń lara Ala la, ń lara;
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na,
Ń lara Ala la, ń lara;
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na,
Ko Krisita bangira dinyɛ na.
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na.

Ń lara Ala la, ń lara;
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na,
Ń lara Ala la, ń lara;
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na,
Ko Kisibaa bangira dinyɛ na,
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na.

Ń lara Ala la, ń lara;
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na,
Ń lara Ala la, ń lara;
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na,
Ko Ala Deen bangira dinyɛ na,
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na.

Ń lara Ala la, ń lara;
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na,
Ń lara Ala la, ń lara;
Ń lara Ala ka kuma na,
Ko Dawuda bonsɔn na bangi min?
U ko Zude Bɛtilehɛm.
